    "cv_train_side_cindex": "0.938 \u00b1 0.052 (5-fold \u00d7 10-repeat, drop_missing_death) \u2014 see reports/phase2_cv_results.csv. Note: XGB-Cox on the same feature set gives 0.980 \u00b1 0.014; Coxnet selected here for monotone-linear interpretability of the leakage signal."
